channel.title: Server status
channel.description:
Has anyone else had problems posting their server under the mopar server status page?
I've done this plenty of times before but for some reason it doesn't seem to be working anymore
It says I've successfully posted the server and then when the list updates every 30 minutes it doesn't show up and it lets me post it again so I know it was removed or not accepted onto the list.
I know my server is online because people have logged on while this problem has been happening.
Does anyone know what's wrong?
